---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
const requestUrl="https://github.com/yansircc/pipee/issues/new?template=extension-request.yml";
const examples=[{name:"飞书",category:"消息与协作",detail:"读取文档、发送消息、跟进群内任务"},{name:"Notion",category:"知识管理",detail:"让 Pi 查询、整理和更新团队知识库"},{name:"Shopify",category:"电商",detail:"查看订单、商品变化与运营数据"},{name:"Linear",category:"开发协作",detail:"从 Session 创建、跟进并关闭 issue"}];
---
<BaseLayout title="Extension 需求 — Pipee" description="提交希望 Pi 获得的新能力。"><div class="page"><section class="content-hero pad"><span class="eyebrow">Extension requests</span><div><h1>描述目标，不必先选择工具。</h1><p>真实需求记录在 GitHub Issues 中，开发者可以看到上下文、补充问题并公开跟进。</p><div class="request-action"><a class="button dark" href={requestUrl}>提交 Extension 需求 <span>↗</span></a><small>将在 GitHub 打开结构化 Issue 模板</small></div></div></section><section class="examples pad content-section"><div class="content-section-head"><span class="eyebrow">Good requests</span><div><h2>先说要完成什么。</h2><p>一个好请求包含目标、涉及的服务、当前阻碍和可验证的完成条件，而不是先指定实现。</p></div></div><div class="example-list">{examples.map((item)=><article class="surface"><span>{item.category}</span><h3>{item.name}</h3><p>{item.detail}</p><a href={requestUrl}>用模板提交相似需求 →</a></article>)}</div></section><section class="request-footer pad"><div><span class="eyebrow">For builders</span><h2>想实现其中一项？</h2><p>从运行时能力开始，再决定是否需要 Pipee Web Surface。</p></div><a class="button" href="/developers">阅读开发指南 <span>→</span></a></section></div></BaseLayout>
<style>.request-action{align-items:center;display:flex;gap:18px;margin-top:34px}.request-action small{color:var(--dim);font-size:10px}.examples{background:#eeeeeb}.example-list{display:grid;gap:10px;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}.example-list article{padding:26px}.example-list article>span{color:var(--blue);font:700 8px var(--mono);text-transform:uppercase}.example-list h3{font-size:24px;margin:30px 0 8px}.example-list p{color:var(--muted);font-size:12px;line-height:1.7}.example-list a{display:inline-block;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;margin-top:22px}.request-footer{align-items:end;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding-bottom:90px;padding-top:90px}.request-footer h2{font-size:clamp(38px,5vw,64px);letter-spacing:-.06em;margin:30px 0 14px}.request-footer p{color:var(--muted);font-size:13px}@media(max-width:700px){.request-action{align-items:flex-start;flex-direction:column}.example-list{grid-template-columns:1fr}.request-footer{align-items:flex-start;flex-direction:column;gap:35px}}</style>
